Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.82,1:53:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take karmic research to see why she was prone to it.\NSometimes after brain injuries, after head injuries, under conditions of extremity, conditions of intoxication, post convulsive fugue, F-U-G-E episodes.
